    • Method Detail

      • getContents

        AdminContentSearchResult getContents(AdminContentSearch search,
                                     AdminDataDescriptor dataDesc)
                              throws KKAdminException
        Returns an array of content records matching the search criteria. If no records are found an empty array is returned.
        Parameters:
        search - an AdminContentSearch object
        dataDesc - an AdminDataDescriptor object
        Returns:
        Returns an AdminContentSearchResult object containing an array of content records matching the search criteria. If there are no records an empty array is returned within the AdminContentSearchResult.
        Throws:
        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine

        contentId - the id of the Content
        Returns:
        Returns an AdminContent object if it exists, otherwise it returns null

        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine

      • insertContent

        int insertContent(AdminContent content)
           throws KKAdminException
        Insert an AdminContent object. If the contentId attribute is not equal to 0 or -1 it is inserted otherwise it is updated with the id of the newly-inserted AdminContent object.
        Parameters:
        content - an AdminContent object
        Returns:
        returns the id of the inserted AdminContent
        Throws:
        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine
